snippet: Wrapping paper inspired a new collection of wall coverings.
abstract: Wrapped, company that makes artistic gift wrap and accessories, teams with Blik, producers of decorative wall decals, on new collection of vinyl wall coverings called Blik X Wrapped.
lead_paragraph: Wrapping paper inspired a new collection of wall coverings.
